<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="over-adv">over <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'əʊvə(r)/    美 /'oʊvər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>[表示在空间上从一边到另一边]:</strong></h4>
<ul>
<li>倒下；翻转：</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Try not to knock that vase over.
小心别把花瓶碰倒了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He rolled over and went back to sleep.
他翻了个身又睡着了。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>越过；穿过：</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Let me row you over to the other side of the lake.
我把你摆渡到湖对岸去吧。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>在那边；在另一处：</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Did you see that building <strong>over there</strong>?
你看到那边的那幢建筑了吗？</p></div>

<ul>
<li>完全地；整个地：</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The lake was frozen over.
湖面完全封冻了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Cover her over with a blanket.
用毯子把她裹住。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>超过；剩下来：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>students of fourteen and over
14岁及以上的学生</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>If there is any food <strong>left over</strong>, put it in the fridge.
如果有剩余的食物，放到冰箱里。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>再一次；又：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He repeated the text several times over until he could remember it.
他把课文重复了几遍，直到能记住为止。</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.★ <strong>结束：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The birthday party is over and we don’t need the cake any more.
生日聚会已经结束，我们不再需要蛋糕了。</p><footer>2012 全国</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="all-over-again">(all) over again</h3>
<p>1.<strong>再一遍；重新：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He did the work so badly that I had to do it all over again myself.
他工作做得太差劲了,我只好亲自重做。</p></div>

<h3 id="over-and-over-again">over and over (again)</h3>
<p>1.<strong>反复；再三：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>As you know, if you do the same thing over and over again, you begin to do it automatically.
你知道，如果反反复复地做同样的事，动作就会变得自如起来。</p><footer>人教⑥ – 3</footer></div></div>